00:42:45,813 --> 00:42:48,733
real fast, and I
saw this guy laying

1035
00:42:48,733 --> 00:42:52,987
on the floor of my
restaurant, the Mambo Cafe.

1036
00:42:52,987 --> 00:42:54,655
Take the four, or
the five, or the six.

1037
00:42:54,655 --> 00:42:56,115
We're on the corner of
108th and 2nd Avenue.

1038
00:42:56,115 --> 00:42:57,492
We're open for lunch.

1039
00:42:57,492 --> 00:42:59,660
-So what you're saying is that
although you had just finished

1040
00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:01,829
