1041
00:43:01,829 --> 00:43:04,791
you were unable to get a good
look at either the assailant

1042
00:43:04,791 --> 00:43:06,834
or their vehicle as
it fled the scene?

1043
00:43:06,834 --> 00:43:08,878
-Yes, uh, these guys were fast.

1044
00:43:08,878 --> 00:43:11,672
All I heard was the
tires screeching

1045
00:43:11,672 --> 00:43:13,883
