1048
00:43:19,639 --> 00:43:21,599
under two months
old eat for free.

1049
00:43:28,105 --> 00:43:30,191
-I don't understand it.

1050
00:43:30,191 --> 00:43:31,192
A guy got hit at what?

1051
00:43:31,192 --> 00:43:32,026
5:00?

1052
00:43:32,026 --> 00:43:33,027
-6:00.

1053
00:43:33,027 --> 00:43:34,111
