1096
00:45:08,664 --> 00:45:10,333
I'm going to go
back to Puerto Rico.

1097
00:45:10,333 --> 00:45:11,918
I'll try to send you the
money from over there.

1098
00:45:11,918 --> 00:45:12,710
OK?

1099
00:45:12,710 --> 00:45:13,753
-What are you talking about?

1100
00:45:13,753 --> 00:45:14,462
Look.

1101
00:45:22,845 --> 00:45:24,305
-We made it!

1102
00:45:24,305 --> 00:45:25,806
