1104
00:45:27,266 --> 00:45:28,726
We did it!

1105
00:45:28,726 --> 00:45:29,685
Oh, thank God.

1106
00:45:29,685 --> 00:45:30,645
We did it!

1107
00:45:30,645 --> 00:45:31,646
-What did you do?

1108
00:45:31,646 --> 00:45:33,105
-We've got customers!

1109
00:45:33,105 --> 00:45:35,066
We've got customers!

1110
00:45:35,066 --> 00:45:36,067
Go check the window.

1111
00:45:36,067 --> 00:45:37,276
Just watch, over there.

1112
00:45:42,323 --> 00:45:44,325
CARMEN: Oh my god!

1113
00:45:44,325 --> 00:45:46,327
They're lined up
and down the street!

1114
00:45:46,327 --> 00:45:47,828
-Tell Ricky and Nydia
to come down here.

1115
00:45:47,828 --> 00:45:48,788
We're going to need some help.

1116
00:45:48,788 --> 00:45:51,290
Ah!

1117
00:45:51,290 --> 00:45:52,291
CARMEN: Ricky, hurry up.

1118
00:45:52,291 --> 00:45:54,293
Go look, there's customers!

1119
00:45:54,293 --> 00:45:55,753
-We did it!

1120
00:45:55,753 --> 00:45:57,254
We got customers!

1121
00:45:57,254 --> 00:45:58,673
-[squeal]

1122
00:45:58,673 --> 00:45:59,757
-Nydia.

1123
00:45:59,757 --> 00:46:00,800
Nydia, go upstairs,
get your clothes on

1124
00:46:00,800 --> 00:46:03,219
and bring your
papa's pants down.

1125
00:46:03,219 --> 00:46:05,179
-People are getting
inpatient out there.

1126
00:46:05,179 --> 00:46:06,555
-Well, just let 'em in.

1127
00:46:06,555 --> 00:46:07,473
-What are you crazy!

1128
00:46:07,473 --> 00:46:08,265
We're not ready.

1129
00:46:08,265 --> 00:46:09,600
-That's OK.

1130
00:46:09,600 --> 00:46:11,560
I just want to see people in
the restaurant for a change.

1131
00:46:11,560 --> 00:46:12,853
Come on in!

1132
00:46:12,853 --> 00:46:14,689
-I want the table where he
